    "description": "Irony.NetCore is a .NET Core compatible version of the Irony framework initially developed and maintained by Roman Ivantsov. Irony is a development kit for implementing languages on .NET platform. In Irony the target language grammar is coded directly in c# using operator overloading to express grammar constructs. Irony's scanner and parser modules use the grammar encoded as c# class to control the parsing process.",
